==German==
===Preposition===

Two way prepostition taking either the accusative or dative case. Accusative implying motion, (e.g where to?), dative implying location, eg (where?).

'''auf'''
#[[on]]
#[[onto]]

===Interjection===
'''auf!'''
#[[Carry on]]!
#[[have a go]]!

